reviewText: Advertising two DVD's and a Book, and when my order came, it was a "memory stick". Did not receive the product as what was expected in-ordered to play it on a DVD player.

At this time of the year I found this video to be excellent.  It gives me simple, quick and easy ways that I can protect myself self in what would otherwise be a very dangerous situation.  I think every woman should own one and learn these simple techniques that could save her life.
